Script Name: EMA+MACD
Author: kicknoob
Description: A simple script using EMA 25 and EMA 50 with MACD. Enter long when EMA 25 crossover ema 50 and MACD line > 0, enter short when EMA 50 crossover ema 25 and MACD < 0
